{"tid":1035186,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【奪命牛肉球】男童不治小食店好姨難過 日後多提醒小心進食","createTime":"2019-02-24T12:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T14:35:55.000Z","uid":222623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ab88e01b6e485692605d238bba0dce5503edee96","tid":1035186,"uid":222623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:50:07.000Z","msg":"黃大仙一名12歲周姓男學生前日放學後，在黃大仙寓所附近購買小食，疑邊行邊食，在連環咬吃兩粒牛肉球時，突鯁喉窒息暈倒，送院搶救，延至今早8時50分不治。<br />\n一行5人神情哀傷的男童親友下午返回竹園南邨住所，拒絕接受傳媒訪問。而有關小食店女職員好姨，聽到男童不治的消息感到很難過，表示日後會特別提醒小心進食，及剪開大件的食物。<br />\n小食店位於竹園巿場。好姨日前曾指，周童很有禮貌，亦記起他買了24元食物，警方向她稱現場食物盒遺下共18粒燒賣和魚蛋，故好姨推測，男童只吃了牛肉球出事。<br />\n事發前，男童在小食店以24元買了6粒燒賣、12粒魚蛋和兩粒牛肉球；牛肉球每粒3元，食物分兩盒包起。<br />\nttps://<a href=\"http://today.line.me/HK/article/jq03RK?utm_source=copyshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2Fjq03RK%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare&d=NJeO18TDpfQgexRQIuB%2FGK2paxXJRTFpYESBXKIXFX0%3D&h=7b1ef396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">today.line.me/HK/article/jq03RK?utm_source=copyshare</a>"},{"pid":"fbf839812fc64ba215d0731e77b418a81fa4dead","tid":1035186,"uid":208391,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:55:16.000Z","msg":"24蚊幾抵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  btw rip.."},{"pid":"a0d99ef3123034505158ca8d30b9a928e33a000f","tid":1035186,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:05:05.000Z","msg":"牛肉球每粒三元<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講起好想食番粒"},{"pid":"d9cc27cfd905617b9361846bdae67e265103a4f2","tid":1035186,"uid":126609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:06:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a941d9b746b19ebb5e95ac3d0431f92dc0b01594","tid":1035186,"uid":154224,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T14:35:55.000Z","msg":"唔係牛丸咩"}]}